{"tid":2496051,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實講咁多野歐超聯簡單啲講只係整一個勁過歐聯嘅盃賽+唔比uefa cap水","createTime":"2021-04-19T14:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T15:42:39.000Z","uid":38189,"like":29,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"4f1b701b75a196ce9c21cf973508ede701677418","tid":2496051,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:17:21.000Z","msg":"其實關害死中下游球會咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊年話整歐洲議會聯賽大把人舉腳支持話想睇狼隊vs基達菲  賀芬咸vs般尼呢啲增加娛樂性<br />\n歐聯講真係會少咗人睇，但競爭少咗，波圖賓菲加李城拿坡里可以試下捧杯嘅滋味，好多分組賽第四名嘅球隊有得打下十六強八強，轉播費分紅未必少咗，水平再低啲嘅球會又可以打新歐霸，分分鐘列斯聯呢啲賺錢仲多咗，點解一定話整死中小型球會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最大問題係創始12隊圍威喂姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實無話唔加打得好嘅球隊入嚟"},{"pid":"5ded9ca2ac4a4f41880a71f01bcf627e7c111a2c","tid":2496051,"uid":343520,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:18:42.000Z","msg":"主要係唔想睇羅馬呢啲所謂強隊"},{"pid":"2b1171dfca87e6e9953cb5786072d794553d6129","tid":2496051,"uid":1991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"垃圾賓 呢次我就撐你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdfe9b0ee5b6e4e11d04ee474f44670c546b928","tid":2496051,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b1171dfca87e6e9953cb5786072d794553d6129","tid":2496051,"uid":1991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"垃圾賓 呢次我就撐你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:19:59.000Z","msg":"撐就推啦 thx"},{"pid":"e95bb2fcd3ead326bfd6c794d4e131c77d695b6a","tid":2496051,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ded9ca2ac4a4f41880a71f01bcf627e7c111a2c","tid":2496051,"uid":343520,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:18:42.000Z","msg":"主要係